                    <note>Fiey provides the following bibliographic citations: <quote source="#bib8-7">AMS, II, 260- 75 ; BHO, 772.
ASMO, 66- 79 ; Lagrange, 65-73 ; Leclercq, III, 169-75.
Suhadii', I, 26D-68.
Fiey, Jalons, 72-75 ; idem, "Elam" (1970), 141-42.
BSCO, IX, 482- 84 (J.-M. Sauget).</quote>
                    </note>
                    <note type="disambiguation">With the priest Aboursam and the deacon Sinai.</note>
                    <note>Lagrange, 65-73</note>
